Class ArraySpectrum

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.Spectrums.Spectrum
      • mixdb.ArraySpectrum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Spectrum>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayTheoreticalSpectrum

    public class ArraySpectrum
extends Spectrum
    An implementation of the spectrum back by an array. The spectrum is basically a arrays of mass and intensity information This allow for much faster processing and analyzing the spectrum compared to the Peak-objected based spectrum
    Author:
    Jian
